    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >追寻传说中的&quot;始源魔兽&quot;，征程已然开启！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个遍布野生魔兽的世界中—它们是蕴藏巨大力量的神秘生物—你将探索绚丽而诡谲的地域，迎战凶悍的魔兽，并构筑属于自己的终极卡组。不同于逐张出牌的传统玩法，你需将卡牌组合成<strong>扑克牌型</strong>—对子、同花、葫芦，乃至独创的牌型组合—以此触发爆炸性效果，主宰战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/bbbb7534ee75b239773135778bc862e5.poster.avif?t=1772165256\" width=588 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/bbbb7534ee75b239773135778bc862e5.webm?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/bbbb7534ee75b239773135778bc862e5.mp4?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上史诗般的旅程，揭开&quot;始源魔兽&quot;背后的真相—传说，寻得它者将获得难以想象的力量……而失败者，唯余毁灭。<strong>开辟属于你的道路</strong>，直面传奇强敌，掌握自身命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/09112126df83bdae47857ddfd43fd3cd.poster.avif?t=1772165256\" width=588 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/09112126df83bdae47857ddfd43fd3cd.webm?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/09112126df83bdae47857ddfd43fd3cd.mp4?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并部署<strong>元素令牌</strong>，为你的魔兽与卡牌组合注入超凡之力。这些强大的修饰物能创造颠覆战局的协同效应，重塑战术、强化伤害，或在每一场对决中揭示隐藏的制胜策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/e9df25673bfb0de74fee7ceedb20faa3.poster.avif?t=1772165256\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/e9df25673bfb0de74fee7ceedb20faa3.webm?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/e9df25673bfb0de74fee7ceedb20faa3.mp4?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当压力袭来，<strong>格挡</strong>机制让你即使身处守势也能发起反击。精准把握时机，弹开敌方攻击并吸收其能量—将对手的力量化为己用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/4f9a91ef071c47627fcf5f9a6d0f2dfd.poster.avif?t=1772165256\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/4f9a91ef071c47627fcf5f9a6d0f2dfd.webm?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/4f9a91ef071c47627fcf5f9a6d0f2dfd.mp4?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还在等什么？属于你的魔兽，正在等待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/15a3ce3b373e55bfcb6bb9f8b4cb7a6b.poster.avif?t=1772165256\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305180/extras/15a3ce3b373e55bfcb6bb9f8b4cb7a6b.webm?t=1772165256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>本游戏包含令人不安的内容，可能引发心理不适。建议玩家谨慎体验。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
